hw4_q2

Class GtuDeque<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • hw4_q2.GtuDeque<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements held in this double linked list
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.Deque<E>, java.util.Queue<E>

    public class GtuDeque<E>
extends java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
implements java.util.Deque<E>
    Deque class that implements Deque interface and extends AbstractCollection class. This class holds data type E as a double linked list and also stores removed nodes in a seperate linked list in order to use them later to save time from memory allocation and garbage collection.
    Since:
    2020-04-13
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Berke Belgin
    See Also:
    Deque, AbstractCollection
